txt.en: The Orcs at the Crack's Edge have set up barriers to protect themselves. Tearing them down will show them that there is no protection from the Iron Garrison and its allies.
You have destroyed several Orc-barriers at the Crack's Edge camp.
Orc-barriers can be found at the Crack's Edge in central Nud-melek.
Orc-barriers can be found throughout the Crack's Edge in the centre of Nud-melek.\n\nYou should destroy Orc-barriers.
